Stehlin v. Nash, Warden; Byrd v. Pepersack, Warden; Mangle v. Winsor, Commissioner of the Department of Health and Welfare; and Richardson v. Rhay, Superintendent, Washington State Penitentiary. Petitioners pro se. John M. Dalton, Attorney General of Missouri, and Calvin K. Hamilton, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent in No. 765, Mise. James H.
